00:24:31,624 --> 00:24:32,802
What sort of visitors?

288
00:24:36,776 --> 00:24:39,361
Everyone. Even close relatives.

289
00:24:39,433 --> 00:24:40,862
I couldn't just leave her here.

290
00:24:40,936 --> 00:24:43,108
We understand,
it is very difficult

291
00:24:43,177 --> 00:24:45,795
to leave a loved one
in a new environment for so long,

292
00:24:45,865 --> 00:24:49,061
but most people need
that time to settle in.

293
00:24:49,128 --> 00:24:50,819
Before we had this rule in place,

294
00:24:50,888 --> 00:24:52,481
residents would forget
again and again

295
00:24:52,552 --> 00:24:53,959
why they were being left here.

296
00:24:54,024 --> 00:24:55,104
Whereas we find,

297
00:24:55,176 --> 00:24:57,729
you give them the month
to settle in,

298
00:24:57,800 --> 00:24:59,807
and they're happy as clams.

299
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:05,183
And after that, a little visit home
every now and then, perfectly fine.

