you're supposed to sign

311
00:28:35,497 --> 00:28:38,247
if you decide to go to Meadowlake.

312
00:28:38,313 --> 00:28:40,222
That is exactly
what I have decided.

313
00:28:40,298 --> 00:28:43,014
You were to go and sign these
and leave them there.

314
00:28:43,081 --> 00:28:46,595
I wouldn't be allowed
to visit you for 30 days.

315
00:28:53,449 --> 00:28:58,851
30 days isn't such a long time
after 44 years.

